  <brief_title>Natural History in CCFDN and IBM Syndromes</brief_title>
  <official_title>Retrospective Cohort Study Assessing the Natural Course in Congenital Cataract Facial Dysmorphism Neuropathy Syndrome (CCFDN) and Sporadic and Hereditary Inclusion Body Myopathies (IBM)</official_title>
